Package org.mv.docxtend.eclipse.jface

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JfaceBuilder
    This class contains the following XtendNode methods :

    _AutoCompleteField can be inserted in :Control --->
    _CheckboxCellEditor can be inserted in :Composite --->
    _CheckboxTableViewer can be inserted in :Table --->
    _CheckboxTreeViewer can be inserted in :Composite ---> Tree --->
    _ColorCellEditor can be inserted in :Composite --->
    _ColumnLabelProvider can be inserted in :TableViewerColumn ---> setLabelProvider
    _ComboBoxCellEditor can be inserted in :Composite --->
    _ComboBoxViewerCellEditor can be inserted in :Composite --->
    _ComboViewer can be inserted in :Composite ---> Combo ---> CCombo --->
    _ContentProposalAdapter can be inserted in :Control --->
    _ControlAnimator can be inserted in :Control --->
    _ControlDecoration can be inserted in :Control --->
    _DefaultToolTip can be inserted in :Control --->
    _ListViewer can be inserted in :Composite ---> List --->
    _ProgressIndicator can be inserted in :Composite --->
    _SameShellProvider can be inserted in :Control --->
    _TableLayout can be inserted in :Composite ---> setLayout
    _TableViewer can be inserted in :Composite ---> Table --->
    _TableViewerColumn can be inserted in :TableViewer --->
    _TableViewerFocusCellManager can be inserted in :TableViewer --->
    _TextCellEditor can be inserted in :Composite --->
    _TreeColumnLayout can be inserted in :Composite ---> setLayout
    _TreeViewer can be inserted in :Composite ---> Tree --->
    _TreeViewerColumn can be inserted in :TreeViewer --->
    _TreeViewerFocusCellManager can be inserted in :TreeViewer --->
    This class will be xtend(ed) to a class setting the hierarchical tree of Jface (Standard Widget Toolkit)

    All the xtend(tion) are based upon the "Model Object" (TableViewer ComboEditor ...)
